name: Calf Crack

Introduction

Approach

From highway 12 between Boulder Utah and Escalante take dirt road a couple miles and park at 37.87871, -111.46841.

==Descent= Entry rappel from a bush with a 100' rope leads to several straight forward DC's. Seasonal pool at the bottom adds a full body bridge challenge to stay dry.
